# UI Guidelines

## Design Principles
- Maintain a clean, minimalist interface
- Ensure responsive design for all screen sizes
- Provide clear visual feedback for user actions
- Follow consistent design patterns

## Markdown Support
- Implement full markdown editing capabilities
- Provide real-time markdown preview
- Support common markdown extensions
- Include syntax highlighting

## User Experience
- Minimize loading times and optimize performance
- Implement intuitive navigation
- Provide clear error messages and feedback
- Support keyboard shortcuts for common actions

## LiveView Implementation
- Use LiveView for real-time updates
- Implement proper event handling
- Optimize LiveView performance
- Handle disconnections gracefully
